719633f-a.title: Manhattan: Edgecombe Avenue - 162nd Street (West)
719633f-a.text:
(1)
Edgecombe Ave., west side, south from and including West 162nd Street,
showing the Jumel Mansion (Roger Morris House) in the center of Roger
Morris Park. Buildings on the right are on Jumel Terrace, west side, south
from West 162nd to 160th Streets. Prominent apartment house, (left) is
the Roger Morris, No. 400 West 160th Street at the S.W. corner of Edgecombe
Ave.
October 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

The same, from another angle.
October 1923.

(3)
A view showing the facade, which faces West 160th Street. Edgecombe
Ave. is on the right.
